      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-4 mb-6">How to Build a Mobile App for Grocery Brands</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-8">Grocery shoppers buy every week. Yet most stores still rely on crowded email inboxes and mobile websites to drive customer retention. This outline shows how a fully managed “website-to-app” build with MobiLoud unlocks push-driven repeat revenue – without rebuilding or adding overhead.</p>
